Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.60,0:00:04.67,Default,Offscreen,0000,0000,0000,,The Japan Broadcasting System hired Android Announcer: Maico.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.67,0:00:09.86,Default,Offscreen,0000,0000,0000,,Her voic gives love, courage, and life to the dwindling 21st century radio scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.86,0:00:11.19,Default,Offscreen,0000,0000,0000,,Things are only at the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.47,0:01:44.14,Suga-san,Suga-san,0000,0000,0000,,Man, STAR's autograph is so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.14,0:01:45.31,Suga-san,Suga-san,0000,0000,0000,,So groovy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.31,0:01:46.23,Suga-san,Suga-san,0000,0000,0000,,So quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.23,0:01:48.39,Suga-san,Suga-san,0000,0000,0000,,It's just writing, yet it's still great!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.40,0:01:49.90,Suga-san,Suga-san,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.40,0:01:53.15,Densuke,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,Quit goofing around and finish up the script, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.15,0:01:54.57,Suga-san,Suga-san,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.57,0:01:55.86,Suga-san,Suga-san,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.61,0:02:00.82,Suga-san,Suga-san,0000,0000,0000,,I will quickly write a shining script like STAR.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.41,0:02:03.95,Suga-san,Suga-san,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}STAR, STAR, STAR...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.53,0:02:05.12,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,Suga is finally getting serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.12,0:02:11.75,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I can expect the replay of that legend from 10 years ago, Live! from the North Pole Crossing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.21,0:02:14.21,Densuke,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,There's one unfortunate woman over here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.75,0:02:15.63,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mind her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.63,0:02:17.17,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,They were in completely differnt universes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.17,0:02:19.05,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,Time will solve the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.34,0:02:21.76,Densuke,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,But it was still cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.76,0:02:26.02,Densuke,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,Since STAR came in, the program has been getting record-breaking listener ratings.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.44,0:02:31.27,Maico,Maico,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to be like STAR-san too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.27,0:02:32.56,Densuke,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's the spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.56,0:02:33.02,Maico,Maico,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.28,0:02:40.24,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,STAR, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.24,0:02:42.57,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,He was absolutely real.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.57,0:02:46.35,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,Like Suga, we need to shine too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.29,0:02:52.29,Suga-san,Suga-san,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.29,0:02:53.25,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,It's too early!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.88,0:02:55.09,Suga-san,Suga-san,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.46,0:03:00.38,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,Gentlemen, quit fighting and get back to work...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.14,0:03:03.01,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:06.60,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,This is Kacchin, elite member of the Japan Broadcasting System.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.60,0:03:08.60,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Oh, Katsumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.02,0:03:08.60,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,Who would say that about himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.39,0:03:10.93,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.27,0:03:14.61,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, we'll talk about that later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:17.40,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care which.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.40,0:03:20.11,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,I know! I do think about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:25.99,Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,450)\fs40\bord3\pos(85,330)}I Want to See You Right Now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.11,0:03:21.49,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,It was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.49,0:03:23.36,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hear you out later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:25.62,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hanging up, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.62,0:03:26.58,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I love you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.67,0:03:36.21,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I should organize my papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:38.88,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,Was that your girlfriend, Kacchin?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.88,0:03:39.76,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.05,0:03:42.93,Maico,Maico,0000,0000,0000,,So Kacchin-san has a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.93,0:03:44.89,Maico,Maico,0000,0000,0000,,I'll input that in my memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.89,0:03:46.72,Densuke,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,You actually got one?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.22,0:03:48.76,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.52,0:03:51.39,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,That woman must have given up on life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:52.52,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,What is that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.94,0:03:58.90,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,Falling in love with a man who has no self-direction and who is always sucking up to other people will only make her unhappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.90,0:04:00.94,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be crying later on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.28,0:04:02.15,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,Well, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.15,0:04:05.20,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,The number of women I've forced to cry number as many as there are stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.20,0:04:06.95,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,See? There's another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.87,0:04:09.20,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,Quit lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.95,0:04:12.71,Maico,Maico,0000,0000,0000,,Kacchin-san, you're terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.04,0:04:14.79,Densuke,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.79,0:04:16.96,Densuke,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,Maico-chan's "Don't be naughty" system!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.96,0:04:17.71,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,Nice punch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:19.71,Maico,Maico,0000,0000,0000,,Kacchin-san, you're awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.05,0:04:22.97,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're a rude android.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.97,0:04:26.72,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,I was actually well-known as "Fast-Eater, Kacchin."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:29.89,Suga-san,Suga-san,0000,0000,0000,,What, Kacchin? You got a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.89,0:04:30.72,Suga-san,Suga-san,0000,0000,0000,,That's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.18,0:04:33.18,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.18,0:04:35.14,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,People call her shy and cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.69,0:04:40.15,Suga-san,Suga-san,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.40,0:04:42.48,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that while smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.49,0:04:44.03,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.03,0:04:47.53,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,Kachi-ko, that phone call earlier was from your woman, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.53,0:04:48.70,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.32,0:04:50.83,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,She's shy and cute, so she's popular, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.83,0:04:51.91,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.91,0:04:55.37,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,She's wonderful beauty, who would even trigger the STAR detector.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.37,0:04:56.67,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.67,0:04:59.17,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,Our almighty elite P.R. officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.17,0:05:01.17,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,Ume-san, give him a big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.84,0:05:02.23,Others,Others,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Congrats!{\1a&HFF&\3a&HFF&}Congrats! Congrats!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.23,0:05:02.74,Others,Others,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Congrats! Congrats!{\1a&HFF&\3a&HFF&} Congrats!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.74,0:05:03.67,Others,Others,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Congrats! Congrats! Congrats!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.21,0:05:04.34,Densuke,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.34,0:05:05.47,Maico,Maico,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.47,0:05:06.88,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.89,0:05:12.77,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,I was already popular with Hana-chan and Kiku-chan during kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.77,0:05:16.35,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,My locker was full of love letters in my elementrary school days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.35,0:05:21.73,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,It was so bad that our homeroom teacher had to tell the girls to save their paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.98,0:05:23.28,Densuke,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think it's real?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:27.24,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}During my junior high years, I got fell into a small slump.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.28,0:05:25.28,Maico,Maico,0000,0000,0000,,He is slightly stuttering.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.28,0:05:27.24,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,So he is lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.24,0:05:30.87,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It really was nothing, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.37,0:05:29.24,Izumi-chan,Izumi-chan,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.95,0:05:30.91,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.20,0:05:34.00,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I got over it quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.49,0:05:35.62,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I want to meet this fictitious girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:40.46,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Oh, yes, I joined a voluntary services club then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.87,0:05:37.37,Densuke,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't that be too mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.83,0:05:41.17,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,I never was too fond of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.04,0:05:45.26,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I really didn't like that too much, but I did the work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:45.59,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,It was out of luck that he got assigned here during the staff reassignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.26,0:05:50.39,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Then I showed off what I did, so I got really popular again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.84,0:05:50.34,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good chance to show him who is really the man behind all of our braodcasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.39,0:05:52.85,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm like a hot rod, an ultimate lady killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.64,0:05:51.68,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Ume-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.47,0:05:54.68,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.02,0:05:57.81,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,I sure would like to see Kacchin-sama's girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.60,0:06:03.02,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,I sure would love to see that wonderful beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.32,0:06:03.80,Others,Others,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:04.51,Others,Others,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see!   I wanna see!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:05.36,Others,Others,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see!   I wanna see!   I wanna see!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:06.17,Others,Others,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I wanna see!      {\1a&HFF&\3a&HFF&}I wanna see!      I wanna see!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:06.84,Others,Others,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I wanna see!      I wanna see!      {\1a&HFF&\3a&HFF&}I wanna see!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:08.53,Others,Others,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I wanna see!      I wanna see!      I wanna see!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.07,0:06:08.53,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,But she's a working woman too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.53,0:06:10.66,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,I really can't make her come here so suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.99,0:06:13.28,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she totally devoted to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:14.91,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.91,0:06:16.70,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,Of course she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:18.91,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should be able to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.92,0:06:20.50,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.34,0:06:30.43,Katsumi,Katsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave a message, then press "#" twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.59,0:06:33.43,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, she only has a pager.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.43,0:06:36.81,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll leave my number, but I don't know if she'll call back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:39.10,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,W-what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.19,0:06:46.69,Izumi-chan,Izumi-chan,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.07,0:06:52.20,Katsumi,Katsumi,0000,0000,0000,,The message has been accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:53.87,Katsumi,Katsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Please hang up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.59,0:06:55.60,Opaq,Opaq,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fnArial\fs15\3c&HF4F4E6&\pos(182,158)\c&HF4F4E6&}!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\N!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.59,0:06:55.60,Default,Message,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fnArial\fs15\3c&HF4F4E6&\pos(182,158)\shad0\c&H000000&}Communication\NEnded
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:07:00.46,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wait around, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.83,0:07:02.75,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,In the middle of the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.75,0:07:05.25,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,She will come, if she's totally devoted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.68,0:07:14.01,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she's not coming, no matter how long we wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.01,0:07:15.72,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,She's not coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:18.02,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's Kacchin's girlfriend, put "-ko" on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.68,0:07:22.69,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,would ka******* be her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.69,0:07:24.69,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.69,0:07:25.56,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.57,0:07:26.77,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,I really believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.78,0:07:27.52,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,She will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.82,0:07:29.53,Izumi-chan,Izumi-chan,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.20,0:07:32.49,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,Even if that's true, I still believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.99,0:07:35.49,Densuke,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,He's so desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.49,0:07:37.74,Densuke,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same thing as saying he doesn't have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:41.50,Suga-san,Suga-san,0000,0000,0000,,My writing gets better when I see other people's misfortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:43.00,Suga-san,Suga-san,0000,0000,0000,,I think I can write a good script.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.25,0:07:45.04,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's been 2 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:46.38,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,Spill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.38,0:07:47.63,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,You'll feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.63,0:07:49.51,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,So? P.R. Officer-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:50.44,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.47,0:07:51.97,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.72,0:07:53.68,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,I...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.93,0:07:56.68,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,What is this music?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.68,0:07:57.55,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,Is it you, Ume-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.18,0:08:01.73,Densuke,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,It's from the STAR detector.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.81,0:08:02.52,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:04.40,Densuke,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,It's responding to something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:06.56,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,Is STAR's official coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.69,0:08:10.53,Maico,Maico,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Kacchin-san's girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.99,0:08:13.03,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.53,0:08:18.03,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,Now you see that my girlfriend is a wonderful beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.41,0:08:24.50,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,I was jsut playing around, trying to create the mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.38,0:08:31.46,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.46,0:08:32.84,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,I absolutely don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.09,0:08:39.05,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know who you are, but thank you for coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:42.31,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now I can keep my pride as a P.R. officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.56,0:08:44.94,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shkow it to that Forehead Man,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.35,0:08:46.40,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Macho Mixer,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.90,0:08:47.35,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Android,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.81,0:08:49.11,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dumped-by-STAR,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.52,0:08:50.57,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Useless A.D.,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.07,0:08:51.61,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and Idiot Script Writer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.61,0:08:54.53,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,I can stick it to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.45,0:08:57.28,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,He's saying it out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.28,0:08:59.07,Densuke,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,He's really out of his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:01.58,Suga-san,Suga-san,0000,0000,0000,,I'm stuck all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:04.58,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, my honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:09.50,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,I see! It was you, Masudamasu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:12.38,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,You always acted cold, but deep inside, you were always...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.38,0:09:14.09,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,Masudamasu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.68,0:09:17.59,Masudamasu-san,Masudamasu-san,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.39,0:09:19.26,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:21.64,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.64,0:09:23.93,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,I am a lady killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.02,0:09:27.14,Densuke,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting so pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.11,0:09:39.70,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,Now you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.70,0:09:41.74,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,You are not a miracle man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.74,0:09:44.04,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,You're a no-good man, who doesn't even have a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.70,0:09:46.66,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.50,0:09:49.63,Suga-san,Suga-san,0000,0000,0000,,Massan, keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.09,0:09:52.59,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have a girlfriend, do you, Kacchin?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.42,0:09:56.72,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.30,0:09:59.59,Maico,Maico,0000,0000,0000,,How terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.56,0:10:06.64,Densuke,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that enough, Matsu-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.94,0:10:09.02,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,There is no giving in in radio broadcasting!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.02,0:10:11.06,Densuke,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,We're not on the radio!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.06,0:10:11.94,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.27,0:10:13.65,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,Am I not right, Kacchin?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.90,0:10:15.61,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,You're a liar, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:21.28,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,You're righ...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:22.16,Maico,Maico,0000,0000,0000,,Kaccin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.58,0:10:33.42,Maico,Maico,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.05,0:10:35.88,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,Are you my girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.05,0:10:38.05,Maico,Maico,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I am, Kacchin-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.05,0:10:39.63,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,You really came!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.63,0:10:40.38,Maico,Maico,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.34,0:10:43.22,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.97,0:10:47.52,Maico,Maico,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.52,0:10:48.73,Maico,Maico,0000,0000,0000,,I am your girlfriend, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.27,0:10:50.69,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, this is so cheesy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.90,0:10:53.40,Masudamasu-san,Masudamasu-san,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.98,0:10:56.53,Densuke,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,But Maico-chan is so sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.53,0:10:59.40,Densuke,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,She was concerned about Kacchin-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.12,0:11:06.08,Suga-san,Suga-san,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man, I'm back in a slump again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.54,0:11:07.87,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.87,0:11:08.91,Maico,Maico,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Maico.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.83,0:11:12.54,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,S-s-s-see?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.54,0:11:16.38,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,I have a wonderful girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.38,0:11:18.30,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,Am I great?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.30,0:11:19.88,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,Y-yeah, you're great.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.20,0:11:22.68,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,See? See?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.05,0:11:23.80,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.80,0:11:25.30,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:28.89,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,It's so pathetic, I just can't go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.73,0:11:31.89,Maico,Maico,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you, Kacchin-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.90,0:11:33.90,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,It's all because of you, Maico.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.31,0:11:35.69,Massan,Massan,0000,0000,0000,,{\clip(0,451,640,480)\pos(320,460)}Congrats.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.31,0:11:35.69,Masudamasu-san,Masudamasu-san,0000,0000,0000,,{\clip(0,445,640,451)\pos(320,460)}Congrats.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.31,0:11:35.69,Densuke,Densuke,0000,0000,0000,,{\clip(0,432,640,445)\pos(320,460)}Congrats.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.07,0:11:37.73,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.73,0:11:39.53,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,I love you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:41.07,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.36,0:11:42.61,Katsumi,Katsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.78,0:11:45.53,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,K-Katsumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.03,0:11:50.58,Katsumi,Katsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, brother, what's going on, calling me out with the pager?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.58,0:11:54.71,Katsumi,Katsumi,0000,0000,0000,,I sneaked out of school, since you said you wanted to see me right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.71,0:12:01.42,Katsumi,Katsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare smile and say this was just a prank!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.42,0:12:05.01,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,Uhhh, I called my girlfriend, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.01,0:12:07.47,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,That's why Maico came, and... then I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.47,0:12:09.52,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.27,0:12:12.60,Katsumi,Katsumi,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on, brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:16.25,Katsumi,Katsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, everyone, what just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.23,0:12:18.48,Kacchin,Kacchin,0000,0000,0000,,Maico!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.69,0:12:22.57,Maico,Maico,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy for you that your real girlfriend came.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.91,0:12:25.82,Suga-san,Suga-san,0000,0000,0000,,This script came out nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.82,0:12:28.20,Suga-san,Suga-san,0000,0000,0000,,Today's show is going to shine, I guarantee it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.45,0:12:30.22,Suga-san,Suga-san,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:07.07,Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,450)\fs52\bord3\pos(185,160)}Maico's Diary
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:05.49,Masudamasu-san,Masudamasu-san,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Masudamasu, a Chief Director for the Japan Broadcasting System.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:09.16,Masudamasu-san,Masudamasu-san,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, I'm the most supreme being among the staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.49,0:14:13.74,Masudamasu-san,Masudamasu-san,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you come to me if you are interested in the radio industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:17.16,Masudamasu-san,Masudamasu-san,0000,0000,0000,,If you want, wearing a million dollar dress is possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:19.38,Masudamasu-san,Masudamasu-san,0000,0000,0000,,Or you meet the nice STAR too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.38,0:14:21.79,Masudamasu-san,Masudamasu-san,0000,0000,0000,,So? Are you getting excited?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:24.84,Masudamasu-san,Masudamasu-san,0000,0000,0000,,Next time - Android Ana Maico 2010
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:30.72,Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,450)\fs54\bord3\pos(160,290)}Tenpoin S Akira
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:26.59,Masudamasu-san,Masudamasu-san,0000,0000,0000,,Tenpoin S Akira
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.92,0:14:29.01,Masudamasu-san,Masudamasu-san,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It must be our guest's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.74,0:14:24.63,Opaq,Maico's Diary,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H6491A0&\b0\c&H000000&\fnArial Narrow\pos(290,120)\frz15\fs26}Today, I become Kacchin-\N san's girlfriend.\N I became one, since\N Kacchin-san said he wanted\N a girlfriend.\N I don't think the staff\N didn't notice that I was\N his girlfriend.
